&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brivity VA, a brand of PLACE, is looking for a self-starting Lead Generation Specialist to advocate for our client’s business through lead generation and management. The ideal candidate for this position has a can-do attitude, willingness to work alongside the client during business hours, a tireless work ethic, an insatiable appetite for growth, and excellent conversational skills in English.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;What is expected of you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and optimize Brivity CRM to improve the operational activities of the Client based on priorities, including lead generation and database management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect for new clients on a daily basis from various lead sources via phone calls, chats, and/or emails.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to incoming leads from internet sources, referrals, sign calls, etc via phone calls, chats, and/or emails.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Input information into the database and create an effective touchpoint mechanism for these leads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct lead follow-up and nurture until appointments are set via phone calls, chats, and/or emails.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure conversion ratios and meet performance benchmarks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you need to possess&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Associate or Bachelor’s degree in any field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior telemarketing experience is preferred but not required&lt;/li&gt;
