&lt;p data-start=&quot;24&quot; data-end=&quot;338&quot;&gt;At PLACE, we’re building a category-defining company at the intersection of real estate, technology, and business services. As a profitable, hypergrowth platform on the path to an IPO, we operate at high standards with a team that is scrappy, execution-focused, and committed to doing the best work of our careers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;340&quot; data-end=&quot;682&quot;&gt;This is YOUR CHANCE to help shape the legal backbone of a rapidly scaling platform that supports top real estate teams across the country. As Legal Counsel, you’ll partner closely with business operators, internal leadership, and senior attorneys to support commercial execution, corporate development, and an aggressive acquisition strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;684&quot; data-end=&quot;856&quot;&gt;If you thrive in fast-paced environments, enjoy practical business law, and want hands-on exposure to deals, operations, and AI-enabled legal workflows, this is your PLACE.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-section-id=&quot;9w2tem&quot; data-start=&quot;863&quot; data-end=&quot;883&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who Develops You: &lt;/strong&gt;PLACE General Counsel&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
