&lt;p data-start=&quot;963&quot; data-end=&quot;1266&quot;&gt;You are a business-minded attorney who enjoys being close to the action. You don’t just interpret contracts—you understand how they impact operations, deals, and growth. You’re comfortable working directly with business owners and operators, translating legal complexity into clear, actionable guidance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1268&quot; data-end=&quot;1520&quot;&gt;You are highly organized, responsive, and able to manage multiple priorities in a fast-moving environment without losing attention to detail. You communicate clearly, write well, and know how to build trust across both legal and non-legal stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1522&quot; data-end=&quot;1695&quot;&gt;You are also practical and solutions-oriented. You’re not looking for theoretical legal work; you want to help the business move forward safely, efficiently, and confidently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-section-id=&quot;1fpmidg&quot; data-start=&quot;1702&quot; data-end=&quot;1720&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
