&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;vzjh8u&quot; data-start=&quot;1825&quot; data-end=&quot;1985&quot;&gt;Serve as a legal partner to internal operations teams and external business operators, providing practical guidance on disputes, risk, and compliance issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ol9qk3&quot; data-start=&quot;1986&quot; data-end=&quot;2089&quot;&gt;Support the execution of corporate development initiatives, including acquisitions and integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1o4jr3&quot; data-start=&quot;2090&quot; data-end=&quot;2216&quot;&gt;Assist with legal due diligence for acquisitions, including review of contracts, corporate records, and compliance history&lt;/li&gt;
