&lt;p&gt;You are someone who takes quality personally. You notice the things others miss, you keep your workspace organized even when things are moving fast, and you do not let a high-volume day become an excuse for letting standards slip. You are punctual, self-motivated, and comfortable working with minimal daily direction once you know the workflow. You communicate proactively when something is off rather than waiting for someone else to catch it. You enjoy being part of a team that builds something tangible every day and takes pride in work that goes out the door looking exactly right.&lt;/p&gt;
