&lt;li&gt;Maintain close attention to detail on every order to ensure quality standards are consistently met before anything goes out the door.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support business card design production and other digital print services as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep the production workspace clean, organized, and safe at all times.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate proactively with team members on order status, issues, and priorities so nothing falls through the cracks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 1 year of experience in a print-related production role.&lt;/li&gt;
