&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with digital press and post-press finishing equipment including UV coaters, rotary die cutters, laser cutters, and laminators.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with digital print services including business card design and production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage multiple tasks simultaneously and stay organized in a high-volume environment without sacrificing quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and a genuine commitment to production quality on every order.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear, proactive communication skills and strong active listening.&lt;/li&gt;
