&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brivity VA, a brand of PLACE, is looking for a self-starting Social Media Specialist to advocate for our client’s business through lead generation and social media marketing. The ideal candidate for this position has a can-do attitude, willingness to work alongside the client during business hours, a tireless work ethic, an insatiable appetite for growth, and excellent conversational skills in English.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;What is expected of you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute a comprehensive marketing plan in partnership with the Client and the leadership team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
