&lt;li&gt;Develop and improve marketing collaterals whether for printing or social online networking. This includes designing graphics and editing videos.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the Client’s online presence including social media platforms and business websites.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage marketing analytics to provide insights for reaching new customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee and manage other marketing related activities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you need to possess&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
