&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PLACE is a technology and services platform built to scale the world&#39;s top real estate teams – and our internal businesses are growing just as fast. As a Staff Accountant at PLACE, you will be at the financial core of a dynamic, multi-entity organization on a path to an IPO. This is not a single-company staff accountant role – you will move across multiple business lines, managing the complete accounting cycle for a portfolio of operating companies, rental properties, and small businesses.If you&#39;re energized by complexity, precision, and the opportunity to build expertise across a growing portfolio of entities, this role was designed for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who Develops You: &lt;/strong&gt;Controller&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Multi-Entity Accounting &amp;amp; Bookkeeping&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the complete monthly accounting cycle across multiple business entities simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process bill payments, track deposits, and maintain accurate records across all entities with precision and consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform monthly and quarterly reconciliations across multiple sets of books, ensuring each entity&#39;s financial data is complete and accurate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage monthly and quarterly tie-outs across entities, identifying discrepancies and resolving variances proactively.&lt;/li&gt;
